SECTION 4

API Contract — New Endpoints





4.1 New SAML Endpoints

Method

Path

Description

POST

/v1/workspaces/:id/saml/service-providers

Register a SAML SP (via metadata XML upload or manual config)

GET

/v1/workspaces/:id/saml/service-providers

List all SAML SPs for workspace

GET

/v1/workspaces/:id/saml/service-providers/:sspId

Get SP details + attribute mappings

PATCH

/v1/workspaces/:id/saml/service-providers/:sspId

Update SP config or attribute mappings

DELETE

/v1/workspaces/:id/saml/service-providers/:sspId

Remove SP from realm

